Why do some tech products feel incredible while others are so frustrating to use? In this video, we break down the 7 levels of product design, from tiny visual details to billion-dollar product vision. This is how psychology, interaction design, defaults, and hidden technical decisions quietly shape the products you use every day.

🖖 Hey! I'm Enrico and on this channel I go behind the scenes of the design and psychology and stories behind the tech you use everyday
